collectible.name: WildPartyDAO: 420 Drink
collectible.description:
Minting now at https://www.weknowparties.wtf

This is the future of music utility! The @weknowparties governance voters will be executive producers of every track put out, and also receive a portion of all revenue generated by releases.

We are celebrating WildPartyDAO's first token-gated party at Bitpixi's Bar on May 20th 9pm EST: https://www.voxels.com/play?coords=S@655W,342N,3.5F

If you've ever signed bitpixi's guestbook, this is why you get free drinks. ;D
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f

collectible.name: GG PP
collectible.description: Goblin Grlz available on secondary: https://opensea.io/collection/goblin-grlz Thanks @goblingrlzwtf for the vibes and @weknowparties for bringing the tunes to the token-gated party that happened at Bitpixi's Bar on June 2nd: https://www.voxels.com/play?coords=S@655W,342N,3.5F If you've ever signed bitpixi's guestbook, this is why you get free drinks. So tell me.. is this pink lemonade.. this doesn't.. taste like.. oh it's not lemonade. This is definitely not lemonade. ᵢₜ'ₛ ₜₕₑ ₚₑₑₚₑₑ
